  "texts": [
    "That is, the mask prevents the decoder from computing contextualized value vectors for future tokens while still permitting parallelized matrix operations.",
    "Intuition: During inference, the next token prediction begins with a special start token.",
    "The decoder autoregressively adds each newly predicted token to the output sequence of predictions.",
    "The attention mechanism computes an attention score matrix in parallel by using the input sequence plus all the tokens in the output sequence, including future tokens.",
    "However, the mask produces zeros for contextualized vectors beyond the current position of token prediction."
